          {
            "id": "top-of-mind-paragraph-2",
            "type": "paragraph",
            "segments": [
              {
                "text": "I've also been using Codex more often for practical tasks, especially quick site updates and small maintenance workflows. I've also started using"
              },
              {
                "text": "Conductor",
                "href": "https://www.conductor.build/"
